data.description: Welcome Home to an exceptional 2nd-floor condo offering a harmonious blend of elegance and comfort. This property boasts 2 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, and a host of desirable features, all thoughtfully designed to cater to your lifestyle needs.  Inside, the primary suite is a spacious haven, with no shared walls, featuring an en-suite bathroom and a generous walk-in closet. With this spacious split plan home, the second bedroom is versatile, perfect for guests, a home office, or a child's room.  The convenience continues with a dedicated laundry room, complete with washer/dryer hookups. The well-appointed eat-in kitchen showcases modern appliances, abundant cabinet space, and a cozy breakfast nook. Meanwhile, the inviting sitting room offers a perfect space to unwind and relax.  For those who love to entertain, the elegant formal dining room sets the stage for memorable meals and gatherings. This condo is situated within a community that offers well-maintained common areas, a plenty of parking space, secure entry with an intercom system, and is pet-friendly.  Conveniently located, this property is in close proximity to shopping centers, grocery stores, restaurants, cafes, parks, and public transportation options. Easy access to major highways ensures your commute is a breeze.  Don't miss out on this incredible opportunity to make this condo your new home. Contact us today to schedule a private viewing and experience the comfort and convenience of this 2-bedroom, 2-bathroom condo with its laundry room, eat-in kitchen, sitting room, and formal dining room. It's the perfect place to call your own.
